flowchart TD
    A["User asks to share screen"] --> B["Voice tool / reply pipeline<br/>start_screen_watch"]
    B --> C{"Native Discord watch available?"}
    C -->|yes| D["clankvox native stream watch<br/>subscribe + decrypt + decode"]
    C -->|no / fallback| E["ScreenShareSessionManager.createSession()<br/>token + share URL"]
    E --> F["Share page /share/:token<br/>capture loop every keyframeIntervalMs"]
    F --> G["POST /api/voice/share-session/:token/frame"]

    D --> H["Latest frame buffer"]
    G --> H
    H --> I{"brainContextEnabled?"}
    I -->|yes| J["Background scanner<br/>note + sceneChanged"]
    J --> K["Rolling temporal notes"]

    H --> L["Normal voice brain turn"]
    K --> L
    L --> M["Speak or [SKIP]"]

    H --> N{"Autonomous commentary enabled?"}
    J --> N
    N -->|first frame / silence /\nscene change when scanner runs| L

    K --> O["Session recap on watch end"]
    O --> P["One-line memory fact"]
